{"tid":2046735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[煮狗飯成績表]信和酒店盈轉虧 首10個月蝕6810萬元","createTime":"2020-06-01T15:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T15:24:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b150aad62257e4531e943d47158db42fb45d85","tid":2046735,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:07:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1591007677631&amp;issue=20200601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1591007677631%26issue%3D20200601&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns867XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=942856cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1591007677631&amp;issue=20200601</a><br />\n<br />\n信和酒店（1221）發盈警，料受到新型病毒爆發及疫情對跨境及國際旅遊之不利影響下，香港酒店業及集團業務表現受到<br />\n<br />\n負面影響，截至4月底的首十個月錄得約6810萬元淨虧損，上一個財政年度首十個月則錄純利約1.629億元。<br />\n<br />\n集團指，因應現時市場狀況已實施及將繼續採取一切可行措施以應對面臨的挑戰，包括推出具吸引力之計劃及優惠以增加收入，與此同時減少營運成本。<br />\n<br />\n集團的現金狀況強健，並且董事會認為集團整體財務狀況依然穩健。信和酒店將於八月底前公布全年業績。"},{"pid":"74b8429b99fb786a305dbd449ee3c382ac4d2b75","tid":2046735,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:07:19.000Z","msg":"有圖 皇家太平洋幫黑警整小學雞飯盒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1831319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1831319</a>"},{"pid":"19044f16cd6bad0dd6472dfec0cb819a73e242cc","tid":2046735,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個都話蝕  個個都話生意差 <br />\n<br />\n咁啲錢去左邊 ?"},{"pid":"215daba973c76a3befcaf227d71c81b47b9ae3be","tid":2046735,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"樓市繼續破頂 股市大升<br />\n都唔明經濟邊度差"},{"pid":"47dde02b71b826d084f7c0918a4078dbbc03c967","tid":2046735,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-